headline.main: CHIANG AT CAIRO BROKE NEW GROUND; His Roosevelt-Churchill Talk Represented Debut Among the Western Leaders

lead_paragraph: Generalissimo Chiang Kai-shek's Cairo conference with President Roosevelt and Prime Minister Churchill was his first face-to-face meeting with the leaders of great western nations.
